done here, I'm leaving.

269
00:16:57,708 --> 00:16:59,750
Oolong tea, if you please.

270
00:16:59,833 --> 00:17:01,833
Don't you want
something a little stronger?

271
00:17:01,916 --> 00:17:03,083
No.

272
00:17:03,166 --> 00:17:05,750
You come to a
bar and order tea?

273
00:17:05,833 --> 00:17:07,791
You're a bit of a
tease, aren't you, Shu?

274
00:17:07,875 --> 00:17:09,333
I won't have a drink.

275
00:17:09,416 --> 00:17:12,250
So stop. Just say your piece.

276
00:17:13,416 --> 00:17:15,708
There's no piece. Sorry.

277
00:17:17,833 --> 00:17:20,416
Maybe I just wanted
to see you again.

278
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,458
Well, if you're
not going to drink...

279
00:17:24,541 --> 00:17:27,458
How about you take
this girl for a spin?

280
00:17:31,541 --> 00:17:35,208
Pick you up in
Roppongi? Of course. Huh?

281
00:17:35,291 --> 00:17:37,000
