282
00:17:38,291 --> 00:17:42,833
Strange. Maybe Sugi
can enlighten me.

283
00:17:49,625 --> 00:17:53,375
Uh, hey Sugi. You're trailing
Shu currently, aren'tcha?

284
00:17:53,458 --> 00:17:55,625
He wants me to bring
the car down to Roppongi,

285
00:17:55,708 --> 00:17:57,791
but he was being vague.
Thought he might be with that

286
00:17:57,875 --> 00:18:02,000
mystery girl of his. If so, make
sure you get some clear photos.

287
00:18:02,083 --> 00:18:03,708
