289
00:18:18,708 --> 00:18:21,833
He totally saw! A male Stylish
who makes a prettier girl

290
00:18:21,916 --> 00:18:24,833
than I do saw me
being an absolute dork!

291
00:18:24,916 --> 00:18:28,208
Good job, self! Let's wrap
this ugly, awkward body of ours

292
00:18:28,291 --> 00:18:30,625
