wedding!" Yeah!

294
00:18:32,750 --> 00:18:34,416
That's a great idea!

295
00:18:44,041 --> 00:18:45,458
My head...

296
00:18:46,416 --> 00:18:49,791
Mom... what the heck
is wrong with me tonight?

297
00:18:49,875 --> 00:18:54,666
My heart-rate's funky and I can
hardly breathe. Man, it sucks!

298
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:57,750
And how come Tsukimi was
all dressed up like that, huh?

299
00:18:57,833 --> 00:19:01,125
Wrapped up in a sheet,
with a cloth on her head.

300
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:03,625
A little old to
be playing princess.

301
00:19:03,708 --> 00:19:05,583
But hey,
maybe thanks to me,

302
00:19:05,666 --> 00:19:07,750
she's getting
interested in clothes.

303
00:19:11,916 --> 00:19:13,500
If that's the case...

304
00:19:14,541 --> 00:19:16,791
Wanna know
a secret, Kuranosuke?

305
00:19:16,875 --> 00:19:19,166
Your mama has a big dream!

306
00:19:19,250 --> 00:19:22,791
Here it is! Mama wants to pack
this closet to the gills with

307
00:19:22,875 --> 00:19:26,375
beautiful dresses
from all over the world!

308
00:19:29,041 --> 00:19:33,250
If that's the case...
I wonder... How would

309
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:38,166
Tsukimi's face look...
if I showed her Mom's closet?

310
00:19:47,416 --> 00:19:52,250
Even if I ever met the right
guy and Mom were still alive...

311
00:19:52,333 --> 00:19:53,833
and she made me a dress of

312
00:19:53,916 --> 00:19:56,833
snow-white lace
like that jellyfish,

313
00:19:56,916 --> 00:20:00,500
it wouldn't even look good on
me. I'd have to be all slender

314
00:20:00,583 --> 00:20:04,958
and pale with big
eyes and long lashes...

315
00:20:11,125 --> 00:20:15,541
I'd have to look...
like him, basically.

316
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,791
Aw, come on! Stop
spazzing out on me!

317
00:20:25,875 --> 00:20:27,333
And you dropped this!

318
00:20:29,041 --> 00:20:31,041
I don't want that old
thing. Jus' throw it away!

319
00:20:31,125 --> 00:20:32,833
Hey, it's nothing to
be embarrassed about!

320
00:20:32,916 --> 00:20:34,916
Every girl plays
"one-woman fashion show"

321
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:37,208
now and then,
right? No worries!

322
00:20:37,291 --> 00:20:39,250
Well, I wasn't having
a fashion show, okay?!

323
00:20:39,333 --> 00:20:41,083
My mom told me
something a long time ago

324
00:20:41,166 --> 00:20:43,750
and I was testing a hypothesis.
It's perfectly rational!

325
00:20:43,833 --> 00:20:44,750
What'd she say?

326
00:20:44,833 --> 00:20:46,625
Back when my mom
was still alive...

327
00:20:46,708 --> 00:20:49,750
she promised to make me
a dress like a jellyfish!

328
00:20:51,708 --> 00:20:53,708
I hadn't thought
about it in a while,

329
00:20:53,791 --> 00:20:55,625
but making all those
dolls this afternoon...

330
00:20:55,708 --> 00:20:57,916
I... I remembered, and...

331
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,291
Tsukimi...

332
00:20:59,375 --> 00:21:01,416
