Please don't tell the others!

333
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:04,666
Tsukimi! Let's make one!

334
00:21:05,833 --> 00:21:08,125
Let's make one! You and me!

335
00:21:09,500 --> 00:21:12,333
We'll mass-produce 'em!
Sell 'em by the truckload!

336
00:21:12,416 --> 00:21:15,666
We'll be filthy rich, thanks
to your jellyfish dress!

337
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:18,458
Uh, hold on. Wha...
whaddya mean, we're going to

338
00:21:18,541 --> 00:21:19,833
make the dress?

339
00:21:19,916 --> 00:21:23,500
We'll take all the money
we earn and buy this place!

